1
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:33,480
Move it

2
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,280
Move

3
00:01:36,510 --> 00:01:37,920
Since Ma the Tiger took charge,

4
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,280
we haven't kidnapped any women.

5
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,790
Now we've snatched two at once.

6
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:42,040
I'm afraid there'll be trouble.

7
00:01:43,150 --> 00:01:44,280
What are you scared of?

8
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,150
Ma the Tiger is human,

9
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:46,400
and we're human too, aren't we?

10
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:47,230
Exactly.

11
00:01:47,230 --> 00:01:48,480
We envy Ma the Tiger having fun every day.

12
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,870
We gotta satisfy our cravings too.

13
00:01:50,230 --> 00:01:50,950
Move.

14
00:01:52,710 --> 00:01:53,230
Move.

15
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:58,480
These two clearly aren't

16
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,070
cheap goods from a brothel.

17
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,070
Haven't tasted fresh goods like this in ages.

18
00:02:03,070 --> 00:02:03,640
Move.

19
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:12,430
You're so fair.

20
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,520
Don't come over!

21
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,150
Good fellows...

22
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,310
we're here to find someone.

23
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:18,470
Did you hear that?

24
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:19,840
She called us good fellows.

25
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,280
We'll find him for you in bed.

26
00:02:24,470 --> 00:02:25,400
Don't come any closer!

27
00:02:25,870 --> 00:02:26,560
If you come closer...

28
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,280
I'll die right in front of you!

29
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,840
It'd be a shame if you died.

30
00:02:30,030 --> 00:02:30,590
That's right.

31
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,680
Don't come over!

32
00:02:32,910 --> 00:02:33,710
Don't come over!

33
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:35,310
I just love this type.

34
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:37,030
Who's screaming about dying out here?

35
00:02:37,470 --> 00:02:38,360
What a racket.

36
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,560
Yu Zhen!

37
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,470
Xiu Gu!

38
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,120
Sha'er!

39
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,280
I finally found you.

40
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:53,680
Why did you...

41
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,560
run off all by yourself?

42
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,960
You've been gone so long

43
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:58,680
without a single word.

44
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,000
I couldn't eat or sleep well.

45
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,280
Fan Bao said he saw you,

46
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,400
so I came to find you right away.

47
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:08,080
Let me see. Let me see.

48
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:10,630
Why are you holding this?

49
00:03:10,750 --> 00:03:11,870
This isn't suitable for you.

50
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,120
Let me look at you.

51
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,240
It's still my Yu Zhen.

52
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,870
It's really my Yu Zhen.

53
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:20,710
From now on,

54
00:03:20,870 --> 00:03:22,590
don't leave me alone again.

55
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:23,240
I won't. I won't.

56
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,590
I never want to be apart from you again.

57
00:03:24,590 --> 00:03:25,190
I won't.

58
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,280
We won't be apart.

59
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,560
Absolutely won't be apart.

60
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,590
Boss Ma,

61
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:34,800
let me introduce you.

62
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:36,430
This is my Wife.

63
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,910
So it's you.

64
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:45,360
And who are you?

65
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:46,630
I am...

66
00:03:47,150 --> 00:03:48,080
Xiu Gu.

67
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,360
Are you a relative of his?

68
00:03:55,470 --> 00:03:56,150
No.

69
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:57,280
A friend?

70
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:01,520
No.

71
00:04:02,150 --> 00:04:03,190
Since you're neither...

72
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,150
Do you know what place this is?

73
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,240
And you still dare to come?

74
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:07,870
Then I'll take her...

75
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,560
...and reward her to the brothers.

76
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,120
Thank you, Boss Ma.

77
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,710
Great! Great!

78
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:13,870
Stop yelling!

79
00:04:14,310 --> 00:04:15,310
What a racket.

80
00:04:17,030 --> 00:04:17,750
You can't do that.

81
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:18,750
Why not?

82
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:21,960
Just wait a moment.

83
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,190
Yu Zhen.

84
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:26,870
During the time I've been away...

85
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,950
...I've been with Xiu Gu the whole time.

86
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:30,800
The two of us...

87
00:04:32,870 --> 00:04:33,480
Huh?

88
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:36,270
Could you...

89
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:37,750
Huh?

90
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:41,560
Is it possible for her...

91
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,270
Oh.

92
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,240
I want to marry Brother Fan.

93
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,240
Didn't you say...

94
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,070
...you only love Yu Zhen?

95
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:53,750
Didn't you say...

96
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:55,680
...you'd be willing to die for her?

97
00:04:56,390 --> 00:04:57,430
I thought...

98
00:04:57,510 --> 00:05:00,070
...you were devoted to your wife...

99
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:01,600
...for your whole life.

100
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:04,000
But you still want a concubine.

101
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:08,070
Men are all the same.

102
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:09,680
Phony and hypocritical.

103
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,800
That's not absolute.

104
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:14,000
There are exceptions.

105
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:17,390
Since you want to marry...

106
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:18,920
...then marry me too.

107
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,720
That won't do.

108
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:23,870
You haven't forgotten...

109
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,510
...what happened that night, have you?

110
00:05:28,310 --> 00:05:29,430
That night...

111
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:32,510
...we didn't do anything at all.

112
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,190
You know which night I'm talking about.

113
00:05:36,510 --> 00:05:37,830
Seems you do remember.

114
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,720
Senior Brother.

115
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:40,720
Say something.

116
00:05:43,950 --> 00:05:45,310
Although I really want to believe you...

117
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:47,870
...I have to believe Boss Ma.

118
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:50,510
Scarface.

119
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:51,800
What are you laughing at?

120
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:56,070
A grown man should own up to his actions.

121
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,270
Troublemaker.

122
00:05:59,310 --> 00:06:00,680
Yu Zhen, Xiu Gu.

123
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,360
Don't worry.

124
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,240
She and I...

125
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:05,510
...really didn't do anything at all.

126
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:07,070
Sha'er.

127
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:08,950
Whether you did or not...

128
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,430
...you're coming back with me.

129
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:12,800
We're going back to Weiyuan.

130
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,870
Everything here...

131
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,040
...I don't care about any of it.

132
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:17,870
Brother Fan.

133
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:20,000
The Huos killed my father.

134
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,190
I had no choice but to come find you.

135
00:06:23,070 --> 00:06:24,390
Your father died?

136
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,310
Let's go.

137
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:27,040
Down the mountain.

138
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,680
Trying to leave again?

139
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:32,830
What?

140
00:06:33,390 --> 00:06:34,190
What?

141
00:06:38,270 --> 00:06:39,600
I won't go! I won't go!

142
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,480
Just let the two of them go.

143
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:44,270
Can't you two have some backbone?

144
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,870
He's out there living free and easy.

145
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:47,360
While you stay home living like widows.

146
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:49,270
Do you want to rely on him that much?

147
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:50,830
I am his wife.

148
00:06:51,430 --> 00:06:52,240
I know him.

149
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:54,000
He never belonged here to begin with.

150
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:55,430
Please let us go.

151
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,000
I promise that once we're out,

152
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,070
about the things here,

153
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,120
we won't say a word.

154
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:01,360
You enter my stronghold and think you can leave?

155
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,560
Not likely.

156
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,720
Sister Yu Zhen, don't beg her.

157
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:07,120
Kill or torture us as you please.

158
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,000
To walk the road to the underworld with Brother Fan,

159
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:09,920
I'm actually not afraid.

160
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,720
My father is waiting down there too.

161
00:07:11,870 --> 00:07:13,360
You sure talk tough.

162
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,600
Then I'll grant your wish.

163
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,310
Don't believe her.

164
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:18,510
She's just talking nonsense.

165
00:07:19,190 --> 00:07:20,070
Don't believe her?

166
00:07:21,190 --> 00:07:22,240
Can't bear to lose this one, huh?

167
00:07:22,430 --> 00:07:23,160
Then what about this one?

168
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,750
Boss Ma.

169
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,600
What is it?

170
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,070
One gun,

171
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:35,000
pointing at two defenseless, weak women.

172
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,480
What is the meaning of this?

173
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,000
Those two are weak women.

174
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,600
Then what about me?

175
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:40,870
In my heart, you are

176
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:42,120
a woman like a little bird.

177
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:44,360
Don't get so excited.

178
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,240
Let's talk this over nicely.

179
00:07:45,750 --> 00:07:46,360
Move aside.

180
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,680
I've already pulled my gun out.

181
00:07:51,190 --> 00:07:52,630
If someone doesn't die today,

182
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,510
my hand will be itching.

183
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,480
Fine.

184
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,160
If someone really has to die,

185
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:00,920
then kill me.

186
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,360
Playing the hero saving the beauty, huh?

187
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:04,360
Then I'll grant your wish.

188
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,240
If you're going to kill him,

189
00:08:05,430 --> 00:08:06,630
then kill me along with him.

190
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:08,120
I don't want to live alone either.

191
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:09,510
You two silly women.

192
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:11,510
You're devoted to him heart and soul,

193
00:08:12,070 --> 00:08:13,750
but he splits his heart in two.

194
00:08:14,270 --> 00:08:15,510
Even I feel it's unfair for you.

195
00:08:16,310 --> 00:08:17,240
How about this?

196
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:18,680
We get rid of him,

197
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,560
and you two follow me.

198
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,270
In the future, if there are handsome ones,

199
00:08:22,630 --> 00:08:23,560
fit ones,

200
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,600
young ones,

201
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:25,680
you can take your pick.

202
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,950
There are plenty of good days ahead.

203
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:29,950
Why hang yourself on a single tree?

204
00:08:31,950 --> 00:08:33,560
You insist that one of us must die.

205
00:08:34,160 --> 00:08:35,720
It's just because you want to tear us apart.

206
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:37,920
Because you are jealous.

207
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,030
Me? Jealous?

208
00:08:40,550 --> 00:08:41,870
Is there anything I can't get?

209
00:08:42,790 --> 00:08:44,080
Actually, you don't understand at all.

210
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,030
True love

211
00:08:47,030 --> 00:08:47,840
is not selfish.

212
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:49,390
Don't push your luck.

213
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:53,840
Yu Zhen, stop talking.

214
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:57,030
Do you understand?

215
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,600
I live at the river's head

216
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,750
You live at the river's end

217
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:05,000
Day after day I think of you but cannot see you

218
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,630
We drink from the same river water

219
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:12,150
When will this water cease?

220
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:16,030
When will this sorrow end?

221
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:24,270
I only wish your heart were like mine

222
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:28,080
And will be true to my love

223
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:33,320
I don't know what you're saying

224
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:36,750
But I can guess what you want to say

225
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:39,910
You people

226
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,440
really aren't afraid to die

227
00:09:43,270 --> 00:09:44,390
It's not death that I fear

228
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,550
I fear never seeing him again

229
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:51,120
I understand those words

230
00:09:53,870 --> 00:09:54,750
I get it

231
00:09:55,630 --> 00:09:56,510
I get it

232
00:09:58,150 --> 00:09:59,150
I know it all

233
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,360
Should we help them?

234
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,750
Are we just going to watch them die?

235
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:05,390
Just say the word, and we'll attack

236
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:06,750
Big Brother

237
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,790
I've been here all along

238
00:10:09,390 --> 00:10:10,360
Ma the Tiger

239
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,080
I like you

240
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:13,960
Shut up

241
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:15,080
No, I won't

242
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:21,480
I know your ruthlessness is just a disguise

243
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:23,320
I know

244
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,750
You act like a man

245
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,360
because you're afraid of being bullied

246
00:10:27,910 --> 00:10:28,440
Shut up

247
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:31,360
I know

248
00:10:32,150 --> 00:10:33,630
You've always been wearing a mask

249
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,910
If you don't want to take it off

250
00:10:36,910 --> 00:10:38,030
I'll stay by your side

251
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,030
Until the day you get tired

252
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:43,030
I will keep you safe

253
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:45,790
I told you to shut up

254
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:47,790
Others laugh at me for being too crazy

255
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:49,480
I laugh at them for not seeing the truth

256
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,150
Ma the Tiger

257
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:54,630
I love you

258
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,150
I said shut the hell up

259
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:08,320
I didn't want to hurt you

260
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:11,150
Tell them to let those two women go

261
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,630
Today, none of you

262
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:14,000
will escape

263
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,440
Let go

264
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:17,840
Let go! Let go! Let go!

265
00:11:20,870 --> 00:11:21,720
Ma the Tiger

266
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:24,240
Who fired that shot?

267
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,120
Ma the Tiger

268
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,200
Ma the Tiger

269
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:42,550
Ma the Tiger

270
00:11:45,390 --> 00:11:46,120
Actually

271
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:48,960
I died a long time ago

272
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,790
That night

273
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,790
what I told you

274
00:11:56,550 --> 00:11:58,080
was all true

275
00:12:10,510 --> 00:12:11,600
It was him

276
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,200
Avenge

277
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,840
me

278
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:17,910
Okay

279
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,480
I will avenge you

280
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:28,080
Let's meet

281
00:12:29,630 --> 00:12:30,840
in the next life

282
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,200
Remember

283
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:35,240
to braid my hair

284
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:38,000
into two pigtails

285
00:12:47,270 --> 00:12:48,270
Ma the Tiger

286
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:56,750
Ma the Tiger

287
00:13:10,270 --> 00:13:11,910
Commander Qin, you're visiting my humble home.

288
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:13,480
Why didn't you let me know beforehand?

289
00:13:13,630 --> 00:13:15,240
So I could have prepared some tea.

290
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,630
I'm not here to drink tea.

291
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:18,480
Then what brings you here, Commander?

292
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:19,840
Let me ask you.

293
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:22,240
Did you have anything to do with Dong Jiuguan's death?

294
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:23,200
Who died?

295
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:24,670
Dong Jiuguan.

296
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,790
Hasn't Dong Jiuguan always been under

297
00:13:27,790 --> 00:13:28,550
your care, Commander Qin?

298
00:13:28,630 --> 00:13:29,870
How could he have died?

299
00:13:30,910 --> 00:13:33,870
Don't you beat around the bush with me.

300
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,790
Commander Qin.

301
00:13:35,910 --> 00:13:37,510
You're wrongly accusing me.

302
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:40,030
Although I had a grudge against him before,

303
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,510
I did promise you

304
00:13:41,510 --> 00:13:43,600
that I wouldn't pursue it anymore.

305
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:44,600
But surely you can't,

306
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:46,080
just because I had a grudge against him,

307
00:13:46,150 --> 00:13:47,630
blame me for everything

308
00:13:47,630 --> 00:13:49,150
that happens to him later.

309
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:52,150
Our Huo Family's caravan

310
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:53,720
was robbed by bandits.

311
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:55,550
We suffered heavy losses.

312
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,550
Recently, our young master

313
00:13:57,910 --> 00:14:00,080
has been staying up all night trying

314
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,870
to fill this financial hole.

315
00:14:02,390 --> 00:14:03,720
How could we have the energy

316
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:05,750
to get up to anything else?

317
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:07,150
Exactly.

318
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,510
And what about that Xiu Gu?

319
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:10,000
Is she doing well?

320
00:14:10,150 --> 00:14:11,960
She hasn't gone off to collude with bandits, has she?

321
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:13,320
Listen, Huo.

322
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:15,440
Just because I didn't catch Fan,

323
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:17,150
you think you can cut off my income?

324
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:19,030
You're really ruthless.

325
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:20,120
Commander Qin.

326
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,000
If you don't have evidence,

327
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,510
you shouldn't make wild accusations.

328
00:14:24,910 --> 00:14:27,630
How would our Huo Family dare do that?

329
00:14:34,270 --> 00:14:35,200
Show him out.

330
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:54,910
What do we do now?

331
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,840
There are only two ways.

332
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,870
Either the one who killed the boss becomes the boss,

333
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:00,440
or we kill the one who killed the boss,

334
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,480
and pick a new boss.

335
00:15:01,670 --> 00:15:03,080
I think the first way works.

336
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:05,390
That's how royal usurpations have always been.

337
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,120
I don't think that works.

338
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:09,440
Later on, anyone who wants to be boss will kill the boss.

339
00:15:09,550 --> 00:15:11,030
Who would respect the boss then?

340
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:13,080
Sha'er.

341
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:14,670
What should we do now?

342
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,720
We can't leave now.

343
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:21,550
Everyone, let me say a few words.

344
00:15:22,150 --> 00:15:23,600
What happened today,

345
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,910
everyone saw with their own eyes.

346
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:28,080
Boss Ma actually attacked Big Brother.

347
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:29,910
As for us,

348
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:31,870
she could take our lives at any moment.

349
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,550
Scarface firing that shot,

350
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:35,790
I think it got us out of a tight spot.

351
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:37,600
Ma the Tiger's death,

352
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,440
must have been an accident.

353
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:41,670
My woman died,

354
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:44,720
and you just brush it off like that?

355
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:46,840
No,

356
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,320
since when did she become your woman?

357
00:15:49,790 --> 00:15:51,480
She asked me to comb her braid.

358
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:54,030
Did you hear that?

359
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:58,480
Did you all hear that?

360
00:15:59,510 --> 00:16:01,480
She asked me to comb her braid.

361
00:16:02,030 --> 00:16:03,320
That means she accepted me.

362
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:05,600
As her man,

363
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:09,030
I must kill the one who shot her in the back.

364
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,840
Come on! Do it! Let's see who kills who!

365
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:12,360
Come on! Come!

366
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:13,720
Alright, alright, put it down first.

367
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:16,510
Stop provoking him.

368
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:17,840
Big Brother.

369
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:20,390
I'm sworn brothers with him.

370
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:21,550
Since we are brothers,

371
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:23,510
you two should be brothers too.

372
00:16:24,030 --> 00:16:25,240
You can't touch him.

373
00:16:25,510 --> 00:16:26,870
I didn't swear an oath with him.

374
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:28,600
I am Ma the Tiger's man.

375
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:30,000
I speak for her.

376
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,030
Well, I'm still the strategist.

377
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:33,840
I'm still in charge of you all.

378
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:35,440
Ma the Tiger is dead.

379
00:16:35,750 --> 00:16:37,030
You're no longer the strategist.

380
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:40,030
Put it down.

381
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,720
If I don't count as the strategist,

382
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:43,870
you don't count either.

383
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:44,840
Who's in charge then?

384
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:47,550
A bunch of grown men, fussing like old women.

385
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,390
Why not just fight it out?

386
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:51,320
Whoever wins becomes the boss.

387
00:16:51,670 --> 00:16:52,320
That's right.

388
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:53,790
Pick one to be the boss for now.

389
00:16:53,910 --> 00:16:54,600
Exactly.

390
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:56,120
Fight! Fight! Fight!

391
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,120
I'll do it.

392
00:16:58,910 --> 00:16:59,750
If I win,

393
00:17:00,270 --> 00:17:01,120
he becomes the boss.

394
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,240
You punk.

395
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:03,480
You can't.

396
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:05,390
Your wounds haven't healed yet.

397
00:17:05,670 --> 00:17:07,000
How could you possibly win?

398
00:17:07,150 --> 00:17:07,840
Sit down.

399
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,360
Then I'll make the call.

400
00:17:11,830 --> 00:17:12,590
I'll do it.

401
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:15,480
Sha'er, you can't go.

402
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:19,720
Sister Yu Zhen.

403
00:17:20,070 --> 00:17:20,920
Don't worry.

404
00:17:21,030 --> 00:17:21,960
He can do it.

405
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:23,030
Good.

406
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:25,110
You come.

407
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:27,790
Big Brother, be careful.

408
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:37,070
Heaven is big, earth is big,

409
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,640
brothers are the biggest.

410
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:54,000
Mountains are high, waters are deep,

411
00:17:54,590 --> 00:17:56,350
brotherly love is deep.

412
00:18:01,030 --> 00:18:02,720
Hearts open and true,

413
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:04,550
sharing glory and shame.

414
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,720
Brothers united in heart,

415
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,920
can cut through metal.

416
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,480
Heaven is big, earth is big,

417
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:42,110
aren't brothers the biggest?

418
00:18:50,240 --> 00:18:50,960
Yes!

419
00:18:59,830 --> 00:19:01,200
Me and my brothers,

420
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:03,920
bow to Heaven, Earth, and Guangong.

421
00:19:04,440 --> 00:19:05,830
I won't say more.

422
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:14,790
You remember,

423
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:16,590
we are always good brothers.

424
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:23,110
Walking the Jianghu, what matters most?

425
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:24,640
Righteousness.

426
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:27,550
Righteousness matters most.

427
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:54,070
How do we score this?

428
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:56,030
It's a draw. It's a tie.

429
00:19:56,110 --> 00:19:57,350
Then who gets to be the boss?

430
00:19:58,240 --> 00:19:59,200
Two bosses.

431
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:06,030
If I become the boss...

432
00:20:06,480 --> 00:20:07,510
on future missions,

433
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:09,070
I'll lead the charge.

434
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,350
If I become the boss...

435
00:20:12,310 --> 00:20:14,920
I'll take the brothers down for wine and women regularly.

436
00:20:15,590 --> 00:20:16,880
If I become the boss...

437
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:20,200
the brothers will feast on the best every day.

438
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:22,070
In a word...

439
00:20:22,590 --> 00:20:24,550
Food? You'll eat your fill.

440
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:27,110
Wine? You'll drink your fill.

441
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:29,590
Women? You get first pick.

442
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:30,750
Good! Good!

443
00:20:30,750 --> 00:20:32,160
Senior Brother, I support you!

444
00:20:32,270 --> 00:20:33,590
Good! Good! Good!

445
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:34,920
Senior Brother, we support you!

446
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:35,640
Support you!

447
00:20:35,790 --> 00:20:36,550
Support you!

448
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:38,160
Your turn.

449
00:20:40,310 --> 00:20:41,000
Big Brother.

450
00:20:41,070 --> 00:20:42,030
Rise up!

451
00:20:47,830 --> 00:20:49,000
You'd better hit the gong.

452
00:20:53,590 --> 00:20:54,480
Bandits...

453
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:57,680
are like rats on the street; everyone wants to kill us.

454
00:21:01,510 --> 00:21:02,550
We...

455
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:05,070
bear the stigma of being bandits.

456
00:21:05,510 --> 00:21:07,480
We hide from soldiers and militias.

457
00:21:07,790 --> 00:21:09,720
We can't care for our parents...

458
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:11,310
in their old age or bury them.

459
00:21:12,350 --> 00:21:14,350
Nor can we raise our wives and children.

460
00:21:15,790 --> 00:21:18,240
You can't even find a *wife*, can you?

461
00:21:21,070 --> 00:21:22,070
It looks glorious...

462
00:21:23,070 --> 00:21:25,400
but we could lose our lives at any moment.

463
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:26,680
These things...

464
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:30,110
we know them all too well.

465
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:33,350
What should we do?

466
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:35,030
We must change.

467
00:21:35,790 --> 00:21:38,110
We must turn from dark to light.

468
00:21:38,350 --> 00:21:41,030
We must stop sneaking around and live openly.

469
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:42,790
Who among us isn't...

470
00:21:42,790 --> 00:21:44,830
a man of flesh and blood?

471
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:46,510
Who doesn't want to achieve...

472
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:47,920
something great and heroic?

473
00:21:49,070 --> 00:21:49,720
From now on...

474
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:53,000
I will share weal and woe with you all.

475
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:55,270
We'll live with dignity...

476
00:21:55,510 --> 00:21:57,590
and act with integrity.

477
00:22:54,310 --> 00:22:55,160
Go on.

478
00:23:16,030 --> 00:23:16,720
Today...

479
00:23:16,960 --> 00:23:17,830
Get down, get down, get down.

480
00:23:18,030 --> 00:23:18,920
The hat looks bad.

481
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:23,960
This hat is perfect.

482
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:24,790
Looks good.

483
00:23:25,640 --> 00:23:26,350
Really?

484
00:23:33,270 --> 00:23:34,270
Today...

485
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:37,070
we are no longer bandits.

486
00:23:38,030 --> 00:23:39,880
The banner of our Brotherhood...

487
00:23:40,110 --> 00:23:41,510
has been raised.

488
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:47,550
We must set the rules first.

489
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:55,920
Disloyalty and unfilial piety bring retribution.

490
00:23:56,480 --> 00:23:59,030
Cruelty and injustice mean death.

491
00:23:59,590 --> 00:24:01,830
Betraying brothers means beheading.

492
00:24:02,270 --> 00:24:04,590
Cursing parents means cutting out the tongue.

493
00:24:05,350 --> 00:24:07,720
Break the law and you castrate yourself.

494
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:11,000
Rapists and bullies face the blade.

495
00:24:11,270 --> 00:24:14,510
Backstabbers will be executed.

496
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:18,110
Betraying guests is unforgivable.

497
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:21,200
Corrupting morals is a sin you can't escape.

498
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:24,030
Look...

499
00:24:25,070 --> 00:24:26,240
that's all I can think of for now.

500
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:27,830
When I think of more...

501
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:29,000
I'll add them.

502
00:24:29,510 --> 00:24:32,160
Everyone must memorize this.

503
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:33,350
Good.

504
00:24:40,200 --> 00:24:42,350
Two braids. Looks good.

505
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:03,590
I live at the river's head

506
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:06,960
You live at the river's end

507
00:25:08,590 --> 00:25:10,920
Day after day I think of you but cannot see you

508
00:25:12,070 --> 00:25:14,110
We drink from the same river water

509
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:17,510
When will this water cease?

510
00:25:19,030 --> 00:25:21,550
When will this sorrow end?

511
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:26,350
I only wish your heart is like mine

512
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:30,750
And I will be true to my love

513
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:39,640
That's right

514
00:25:40,240 --> 00:25:41,880
We're going to have a good life

515
00:25:45,350 --> 00:25:46,310
Are you planning

516
00:25:46,550 --> 00:25:48,030
to settle down here for good?

517
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:49,960
This is a lawless zone

518
00:25:50,550 --> 00:25:52,350
We can do whatever we want

519
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:55,830
We'll live free and easy

520
00:25:56,350 --> 00:25:57,350
So, in the future

521
00:25:57,880 --> 00:25:59,000
you're not going back to the Fan family?

522
00:26:00,070 --> 00:26:01,350
Great-Uncle is at home

523
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:03,750
I don't need to worry about him

524
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:06,350
Great-Uncle doesn't even know you're still alive

525
00:26:06,790 --> 00:26:08,160
He's getting old

526
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:11,160
You should go back and do your filial duty

527
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:14,310
I haven't even warmed my throne yet

528
00:26:14,790 --> 00:26:16,350
Haven't had the chance to show off my power

529
00:26:18,070 --> 00:26:19,350
Fan Bao is at home

530
00:26:19,350 --> 00:26:21,030
He's more filial than I am

531
00:26:26,400 --> 00:26:27,160
What's wrong?

532
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:28,830
You're unhappy?

533
00:26:34,550 --> 00:26:38,480
Yu Zhen, let's have some fun

534
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,070
Did you miss me?

535
00:26:59,510 --> 00:27:00,070
Okay

536
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:01,440
I'll go sleep outside

537
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:03,720
You go to bed early

538
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:05,310
Don't catch a cold

539
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:23,000
Brother Fan, why are you here?

540
00:27:26,550 --> 00:27:28,510
Why are you still unhappy even after becoming the boss?

541
00:27:31,640 --> 00:27:32,880
I'm the boss now

542
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:34,510
Who am I afraid of?

543
00:27:37,270 --> 00:27:39,200
You look so handsome as the boss

544
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:41,640
Let me tell you

545
00:27:41,720 --> 00:27:44,200
Before, if I wanted to do anything

546
00:27:45,400 --> 00:27:46,960
I had to watch other people's moods

547
00:27:47,310 --> 00:27:49,590
Now I can finally call the shots myself

548
00:27:50,750 --> 00:27:51,680
Your father

549
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:53,750
died saving Yu Zhen

550
00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:56,480
I will definitely find a way to get revenge

551
00:27:59,310 --> 00:28:01,270
You should go spend more time with Sister Yu Zhen

552
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:02,440
I'll go tomorrow

553
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:06,400
You haven't seen each other for so long

554
00:28:11,880 --> 00:28:12,510
Right

555
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:15,550
You're right

556
00:28:40,070 --> 00:28:41,750
Darn it

557
00:29:07,030 --> 00:29:08,590
Hello, Sister-in-law

558
00:29:10,750 --> 00:29:11,830
What is this for?

559
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:14,000
Taking you home

560
00:29:15,310 --> 00:29:16,110
Really?

561
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,240
Everything is ready

562
00:29:18,790 --> 00:29:19,640
Just waiting for you

563
00:29:21,510 --> 00:29:22,310
So many people

564
00:29:22,590 --> 00:29:23,590
are going back with us?

565
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:25,830
This is called returning home in glory

566
00:29:26,750 --> 00:29:28,270
You should probably keep a low profile

567
00:29:28,550 --> 00:29:30,030
Don't scare Great-Uncle

568
00:29:30,310 --> 00:29:32,200
I just want Great-Uncle

569
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:35,200
to see that I've made something of myself

570
00:29:37,240 --> 00:29:38,110
Then I'll go pack

571
00:29:38,350 --> 00:29:39,590
Pack what?

572
00:29:40,480 --> 00:29:41,200
Let's just go

573
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:42,350
There's everything at home

574
00:29:43,400 --> 00:29:45,240
Xiu Gu, you take that sedan chair

575
00:29:45,480 --> 00:29:46,000
Quick

576
00:29:46,550 --> 00:29:47,350
You take this one

577
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:49,830
Ready

578
00:29:52,510 --> 00:29:53,880
Lift the sedan

579
00:29:55,240 --> 00:29:56,400
Leave the palace

580
00:29:56,790 --> 00:29:57,750
What do you mean "leave the palace"?

